## Overview
This directory contains the official Standard Operating Procedure governing the execution of the month-end close.

The aim is to:

- protect financial integrity  
- ensure completeness and accuracy  
- deliver timely reporting  
- maintain audit defensibility  
- prevent uncontrolled or undocumented changes  

This is the foundation of the finance control environment.

---

## What This SOP Covers
The procedure defines mandatory rules for:

- Roles and responsibilities  
- Task ownership and lifecycle  
- Status progression  
- RAG risk monitoring  
- Evidence standards  
- Estimates and judgement areas  
- Dependency management  
- Post-close adjustment governance  
- Version control  

It applies to **all entities**, **all reporting periods**, and **all close activities**.

