## Control Principles Embedded in This SOP

### 1) Repeatability  
The close must follow a consistent, structured process every month.

### 2) Evidence First  
If a task cannot be supported, it is not complete.

### 3) Independent Review  
Preparation and approval must be segregated.

### 4) Transparency  
Progress, risks, and changes must be visible.

### 5) Controlled Change  
Post-preparation and post-close changes require approval.

